                <origin/>
                <commentary/>
                <excerpt/>
                <transcript/>
                <trailer/>
                <names/>
                <summary>The Panorama of the Arctic region will visit Chambersburg.</summary>
                <note/>
                <look/>
            </div>
            <div type="a">
                <column>02</column>
                <head>Water Works Survey</head>
                <origin/>
                <commentary/>
                <excerpt/>
                <transcript/>
                <trailer/>
                <names/>
                <summary>The Chief Engineer of the Philadelphia Water Works will visit Chambersburg
                    on Monday to make the preliminary examination for the building of the
                    Chambersburg Water Works.</summary>
                <note/>
                <look/>
            </div>
            <div type="a">
                <column>03</column>
                <head>More Incendiarism in Texas</head>
                <origin/>
                <commentary/>
                <excerpt/>
                <transcript/>
                <trailer/>
                <names/>
                <summary>A large number of fires have occurred in Northern Texas. When 20 fires
                    occurred on one day, the people became suspicious and "several individuals, who
                    proved to be Abolitionists, and who were unable to give any satisfactory reason
                    for their presence in the several communities where they were found" were
                    arrested.</summary>
                <note/>
                <look/>
            </div>
            <div type="a">
                <column>03</column>
                <head>Meeting of the Democratic State Committee</head>
                <origin/>
                <commentary/>
                <excerpt/>
                <transcript/>
                <trailer/>
                <names/>
                <summary>Discussion of the meeting of the Pennsylvania Democratic Committee. The
                    article details the struggle between the Douglas and the Breckenridge
                    supporters.</summary>
                <note>Difficult to read.</note>
                <look/>
            </div>
